 hammered surface, with your choice of three chain lengths and four finishes (including a solid-14-karat-gold option). In addition to letters and various fonts, the disk charms are available with tiny stamped illustrations, like hearts, moons, or astrological signs. And you can add other charms, if you choose to. If your MIL prefers more sparkle, consider the <a class="product-link" href="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/61049/200182/4/182903/?merchant=GLDN" rel="noopener sponsored" target="_blank" data-gtm-trigger="product_link" data-store="GLDN" data-pick-type-id="7" data-vars-outbound-link="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/61049/200182/4/182903/?merchant=GLDN" data-vars-store="GLDN" data-gtm-context="chapter_family-jewels" data-gtm-element="product_link_impression" data-link-type="link" data-merchant="GLDN" data-pid="61049" data-url="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/61049/200182/4/182903/?merchant=GLDN">GLDN Aura Pendant Necklace</a>, which uses birthstones instead of alphabet disks to represent loved ones.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="b6d81848 d47f7b03" id="a-place-for-patisserie" expanded=""><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0 e5f9b502"><h2 class="e823fba7" aria-controls="a-place-for-patisserie-panel" aria-selected="true" role="tab" tabindex="0" data-gtm-element="chapter_heading" data-gtm-trigger="single_chapter" data-chapter-name="A place for patisserie" data-expand-close="close" data-chapter-index="2">A place for patisserie</h2></div></div><div id="a-place-for-patisserie-panel" class="fa265be5" aria-labelledby="a-place-for-patisserie" aria-hidden="false" role="tabpanel"><div class=" chapter__content-wrapper"><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0"><figure id="attachment_376713" class="wp-caption alignnone"><div class="ec5f8867 global_chapter__arp_image"><img loading="lazy" alt="A clear pink Fortessa Tableware Solutions Jupiter Hobnail Glass Cake 