 savers" data-expand-close="close" data-chapter-index="11">Sweet savers</h2></div></div><div id="sweet-savers-panel" class="fa265be5" aria-labelledby="sweet-savers" aria-hidden="false" role="tabpanel"><div class=" chapter__content-wrapper"><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0"><figure id="attachment_341656" class="wp-caption alignnone"><div class="ec5f8867 global_chapter__arp_image" style="padding-bottom:66.70%;display:inline"><img alt="Several Stasher Silicone Bags of different sizes and colors, filled with healthy snacks like grapes, green beans and nuts." data-src="https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2023/10/giftspeoplehaveeverything-2048px-stasher.jpg?auto=webp&amp;width=1024" width="1024" height="683" class="cf3feb4c c882c9ce alignnone size-large wp-image-341656" loading="lazy"/></div><figcaption class="wp-caption-text"> <!-- --> <span class="wp-caption-text wp-caption-credit">Photo: Sarah Kobos</span></figcaption></figure></div></div></div><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0"><div class="ebb615ab global-cob e1e566ad" data-scp="callout"><div id="callout-chapter-7-4" class="fd1ac384" data-scp="callout_item" data-testid="callout" data-pid="36211"><span class="ddf294c5"><div class="fabe3ad3"><div class="e14704b2" role="button" tabindex="0" data-gtm-trigger="save_product" data-save-content-value="true" data-save-content-id="36211"><span aria-label="Save Product" class="a478f5d2  " data-gtm-trigger="save_product" data-save-content-value="true" data-save-content-id="36211"></span></div></div></span><div class="f1cabe17"><div class="f31f6df1"><div class="efc734d0 eae76d54"><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/36211/166494/4/173580?merchant=Amazon" class="fa8c1483 product-merchant-link-button" rel="sponsored noreferrer" target="_blank" data-store="Amazon" data-vars-store="Amazon" data-vars-outbound-link="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/36211/166494/4/173580?merchant=Amazon