Shangri-La Robe</a> for anyone who appreciates an extra-soft fabric. The robe’s lightweight jersey drapes flatteringly on a range of body types, and it comes in more size options than most of the competition. It’s soft and comfy for optimal lounging, and in our testing, it still looked brand new after many washes.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="b6d81848 d47f7b03" id="a-handy-scandi-jug" expanded=""><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0 e5f9b502"><h2 class="e823fba7" aria-controls="a-handy-scandi-jug-panel" aria-selected="true" role="tab" tabindex="0" data-gtm-element="chapter_heading" data-gtm-trigger="single_chapter" data-chapter-name="A handy Scandi jug" data-expand-close="close" data-chapter-index="20">A handy Scandi jug</h2></div></div><div id="a-handy-scandi-jug-panel" class="fa265be5" aria-labelledby="a-handy-scandi-jug" aria-hidden="false" role="tabpanel"><div class=" chapter__content-wrapper"><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0"><figure id="attachment_376704" class="wp-caption alignnone"><div class="ec5f8867 global_chapter__arp_image"><img loading="lazy" alt="Three Raawii Strøm Jugs in a small yellow, large red, and medium navy blue." src="https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2024/04/mother-in-law-2048px-3546.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=60&amp;width=265" data-src="https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2024/04/mother-in-law-2048px-3546.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=60&amp;width=570" data-srcset="https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2024/04/mother-in-law-2048px-3546.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=60&amp;width=570 768w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2024/04/mother-in-law-2048px-3546.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=60&amp;width=570&amp;dpr=1.5 1152w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2024/04/mother-in-law-2048px-3546.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=60&amp;width=570&amp;dpr=2 1536w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2024/04/mother-in-law-