ll, since you love your mother-in-law’s grownup child, why not surprise her with a new, lower-maintenance child? If you’re unsure which variety is the best fit for your MIL, start by exploring The Sill’s handy <a class="product-link" href="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/50458/180467/4/145134/?merchant=The%20Sill" rel="noopener sponsored" target="_blank" data-gtm-trigger="product_link" data-store="The Sill" data-vars-outbound-link="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/50458/180467/4/145134/?merchant=The%20Sill" data-vars-store="The Sill" data-gtm-context="chapter_a-plant-for-every-preference" data-gtm-element="product_link_impression" data-link-type="link" data-merchant="The Sill" data-pid="50458" data-url="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/50458/180467/4/145134/?merchant=The%20Sill">easy-care collection</a>. You’ll find a selection of sturdy options suited for beginners, such as snake plants and philodendrons.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="b6d81848 d47f7b03" id="salty-storage" expanded=""><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0 e5f9b502"><h2 class="e823fba7" aria-controls="salty-storage-panel" aria-selected="true" role="tab" tabindex="0" data-gtm-element="chapter_heading" data-gtm-trigger="single_chapter" data-chapter-name="Salty storage" data-expand-close="close" data-chapter-index="22">Salty storage</h2></div></div><div id="salty-storage-panel" class="fa265be5" aria-labelledby="salty-storage" aria-hidden="false" role="tabpanel"><div class=" chapter__content-wrapper"><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0"><figure id="attachment_346400" class="wp-caption alignnone"><div class="ec5f8867 global_chapter__arp_image"><img loading="lazy" alt="A red Emile Henry Salt Pig full of salt, in front of a red background." src="https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2023/11/giftsformotherinlaws-2048px-8396.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=60&amp;width=265" data-src="https://